Problem

System entered unstable stuck-state loop.

Solution

Removed aggressive stuck-state handling.
Simplified to pulse-based logic.

5. BLE starting on every water pulse

Problem

Massive unnecessary BLE wakeups and battery drain.

Solution

BLE decoupled from water activity.
Water only updates counters now.
the previouse versions i made had a flaw, i misunderstood the assignment and activated the ble while water was running 
i removed the ble call from pulse counter and wakeup condition and implemented a data and time based configurable ble wakeup that is
independent from the pulse counter. and it work while water running or not. saving tones of battery
